                  </hi>(<hi rend="italic">police-constable R</hi>184.) I was at Woolwich on the 1st of June—I saw the prisoner near the market-place, where the circus is kept—he was carrying this rope, which I now produce, under his arm—I asked how he came by it—he said his mother gave it him to sell—I took him to his mother—she denied all knowledge of it—I then found the prosecutor.</p>
